{"tid":1161873,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"想請籃球球證","createTime":"2019-05-19T13:08:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T13:33:48.000Z","uid":79172,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e4b676b0b1bb8d95dc10a8a57623c7ea15939ab1","tid":1161873,"uid":79172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T13:08:51.000Z","msg":"聘請Freelance籃球球證，<br />\n條件如下:<br />\n~ 持有或曾持有FIBA球證牌照 (請提供註冊編號以便於HKBA查詢)<br />\n~ 年齡滿18歲<br />\n~ 大專院校學生優先<br />\n~ 男女皆可<br />\n~ 曾於香港籃球總會或各大型非官方籃球賽事擔件裁判至少2年 (請於申請時簡述)<br />\n~ 熟習2人及3人裁判法<br />\n~ 熟習紀錄台紀錄法<br />\n<br />\n有意者可留TG，會進行Phone Interview (cover少量Fiba Official Basketball Rules test)，成功者會於6月1日及6月2日進行場習( 3v3 outdoor salary: 500HKD/4hrs 無需協助場地佈置 )。表現優異者會獲考慮加入本團隊。"},{"pid":"b774fbd5c5ed99efba8e16a6a2e51a83be452e58","tid":1161873,"uid":39215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T13:09:36.000Z","msg":"吹過NBA 請唔請？"},{"pid":"ef730e431ee3adef07ddce24ace56a677cf055ca","tid":1161873,"uid":6964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T13:20:48.000Z","msg":"玩具都要咩牌咩牌？"},{"pid":"821a7dfb6dd415677d3a563fc221aab95a4e39f1","tid":1161873,"uid":71458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T13:33:48.000Z","msg":"全部都係1號 點mark啊"}]}